# <project>/.claude/stacks — override for ~/.claude/hooks/detect-stack.sh
#
# Lists stack-rule files to load from ~/.claude/stack-rules/<name>.md at session start.
# When present, this file COMPLETELY overrides auto-detection.
#
# Format:
#   - one stack name per line, OR comma-separated on a line
#   - '#' starts a line/inline comment
#   - whitespace is trimmed
#
# Available stack names (must match ~/.claude/stack-rules/<name>.md):
#   nodejs, nextjs-react, vuejs, python, java, mongodb

nodejs
mongodb

# Equivalent one-liner:
# nodejs, mongodb

# Examples for other project shapes:
#   Next.js + Mongo:    nextjs-react, nodejs, mongodb
#   Nuxt + Mongo:       vuejs, nodejs, mongodb
#   FastAPI + Mongo:    python, mongodb
#   Spring Boot + Mongo: java, mongodb
